originalText.text:
I made an appointment the first time and when I arrived the person who was supposed to help me had someone else already there and told me to come back another day. I called to make a second appointment and without even listening he rushed me off the phone and said sure come by this date. When the date arrived he said he didn’t remember giving me an appointment and that he had no space whatsoever. This establishment is completely unprofessional and I definitely would never recommend it.

You would think your experience would be better because you interact directly with the owner but no. Very rude and does not understand the value of a customer and the value of a good service going a long way.
